entries.arrival_phase_1: Head out past the Tyyyn nebula. Intercept the arms dealer!
entries.arrival_phase_2: Scan positive! The arms dealer has arrived! Neutralize the target with extreme prejudice.
entries.assassinate_success: Excellent work! It will be a long time before the Ghrag mercenaries can entice another weapons dealer to aid their ruthless cause!
entries.escort_remaining: Ghrag escort fighter eliminated! %DI fighters remaining.
entries.escort_wiped_out: Ghrag escort screen eliminated! Now destroy the weapons dealer!
entries.failed_escape: We lost the weapons dealer! Probably gone back into hiding... Come down and see me. We'll regroup!
entries.quest_location_d: Ghrag mercenaries are escorting a weapons dealer known to the Empire as 'Vosc Traaer.' He is death-marked by the Emperor for embezzling over twenty million credits during his contract.
entries.quest_target_d: The weapons dealer Vosc Traaer is flying under armed escort. Destroy his ship before he reaches his destination.
entries.title: Intercept and Destroy Weapons Dealer
entries.title_d: Prevent the Ghrag mercenaries from acquiring enough munitions to destroy the Imperial space station here in Kashyyyk. Eyma is tracking the dealer based on information provided by the Ghrag traitor you escorted safely out of the system.
